metadata.name: The Frog Prince
metadata.description: once upon a time There was an unfortunate prince who was cursed to become a frog and was alone in a brackish swamp. Until he kisses the princess, his true love is free from the curse. But after so many years, no princess was interested in a simple frog like him. With loneliness, the prince tried to transform his body into a machine and connect to the Internet to access dating sites. But fate brought him into the world of crypto until he became rich by investing in crypto coins. From then on, princesses from all over came to kiss him almost every day. It wasn't a kiss from true love that breaks the curse, but he lives happily as the "Crypto Prince" forever.
